'''''Schitt's Creek''''' is a Canadian television [[sitcom]] which premiered on [[CBC Television]] on January 13, 2015.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/arts/eugene-levy-and-catherine-o-hara-are-up-schitt-s-creek-1.2806231 |title=Eugene Levy and Catherine O'Hara are up Schitt's Creek |date=October 21, 2014 |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=October 21, 2014}}</ref> The series was created by [[Eugene Levy]] and [[Daniel Levy (TV personality)|Daniel Levy]] and produced by Not a Real Company Productions.<ref name="playback">{{cite web |url=http://playbackonline.ca/2014/02/11/sctv-alums-levy-and-ohara-to-star-in-cbc-comedy/ |title="SCTV alums Levy and O<U+2019>Hara to star in CBC comedy" |last=Cummins |first=Julianna |date=February 11, 2014 |publisher=''[[Playback (website)|Playback]]'' |accessdate=January 14, 2015}}</ref> On January 12, 2015, CBC renewed the show for a second season.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/arts/schitt-s-creek-gets-greenlight-for-second-season-1.2895953 |title=Schitt's Creek gets greenlight for second season |date=January 12, 2015 |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=January 12, 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/2015/01/19/schitts-creek-is-off-to-a-dazzling-start-menon.html |title=Schitt<U+2019>s Creek is off to a dazzling start |date=January 19, 2015 |publisher=''[[Toronto Star]]'' |accessdate=January 22, 2015}}</ref>

The series stars Eugene Levy and [[Catherine O'Hara]] as Johnny and Moira Rose, a wealthy couple who are forced, after losing all their money, to rebuild their lives in their only remaining asset: the small town of Schitt's Creek, which they once purchased as a joke.<ref name=weisblott>[http://o.canada.com/entertainment/cbc-schitts-creek/ "SCTV stars Levy and O<U+2019>Hara reunite for a forthcoming CBC sitcom called Schitt<U+2019>s Creek"]. [[canada.com]], February 10, 2014.</ref> The cast also includes Daniel Levy, Annie Murphy, [[Chris Elliott]],<ref name=weisblott /> [[Jennifer Robertson]] and [[Emily Hampshire]].

The series is filmed on location in [[Goodwood, Ontario]] which is located in the [[Regional Municipality of Durham]] of the [[Greater Toronto Area]] while the interior scenes are filmed at [[Pinewood Toronto Studios]] in Toronto.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/television/2015/01/12/how_eugene_levy_convinced_cbc_to_name_his_show_schitts_creek.html |title=How Eugene Levy convinced CBC to name his show <U+2018>Schitt<U+2019>s Creek<U+2019> |last=Wong |first=Tony |date=January 12, 2015 |publisher=Toronto Star |accessdate=January 13, 2015}}</ref>

==Cast and characters==
* [[Eugene Levy]] as Johnny Rose
* [[Catherine O'Hara]] as Moira Rose
* [[Daniel Levy (TV personality)|Daniel Levy]] as David Rose
* Annie Murphy as Alexis Rose
* Sarah Levy as Twyla Sands
* [[Chris Elliott]] as Roland Schitt
* [[Jennifer Robertson]] as Jocelyn Schitt
* [[Emily Hampshire]] as Stevie Budd
* [[Tim Rozon]] as Mutt Schitt

