==Reception==
''Schitt's Creek'' has received generally positive reviews, scoring 62 out of 100 based on ten critics on [[Metacritic]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/schitts-creek/ |title=Schitt's Creek : Season 1 |publisher=Metacritic |accessdate=February 11, 2015}}</ref>

==International broadcast==
The series has been picked up for showing in the United States by [[Pop (U.S. TV channel)|Pop]] (formerly TVGN) and premiered on February 11, 2015.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2014/10/eugene-levy-schitts-creek-series-pop-856574 |title=Pop Picks Up Eugene Levy Comedy <U+2018>Schitt<U+2019>s Creek<U+2019> As First Original Scripted Series |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |date=October 21, 2014 |publisher=Deadline |accessdate=January 8, 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ew.com/article/2014/11/17/tvgn-rebrand-pop-announces-lineup-for-2015-premieres-clip-from-schitts-creek |title=TVGN rebrand Pop announces lineup for 2015, premieres clip from 'Schitt's Creek' |last=Jue |first=Teresa |date=November 17, 2014 |publisher=Entertainment Weekly |accessdate=February 11, 2015}}</ref>

